### PRIVACY POLICY
This privacy policy governs your use of the software application News Pro for mobile devices that was created by Mr. Durgesh Kumar.
News Pro is a News com social newtworking application which gets news from various sources like BBC Hindi, News 18 and others using their RSS Feed.
It also gives social networking features like comment and like news.
User can post their own news too. We do not promote violence by any of our users.
We keep notice of reported comments if it do not follows standard procedures then we can delete them from our own side.
We do not modify or change user comments. We just remove them if it is not standard and if many users has reported them.
We just receive the news from rss feed and display it. For authenticity of any news users have to file complain on their official websites.
This App uses Radio Services as fan basis. 
1. This App is maintained by and is for the use of Vividh Bharti Fans.

2. This App is Not Affiliated to 'Prasar Bharti' or 'All India Radio' in any manner.

3. If you have any questions or concerns regarding content of the website, Please contact Info@vividhbharti.org


### What permissions does News Pro require and why?
News Crow requires the following permissions :

### Photos / Media / Files
*	Read the contents of your USB storage
*	Modify or delete the contents of your USB storage

These permissions are required to post images.
### Storage
*	Read the contents of your USB storage
*	Modify or delete the contents of your USB storage

These permissions are required to get images and compress it before posting.

### Camera
*	Take pictures and videos

These permissions are required by News Crow for two purposes and these two purposes only:
* These permission are required to click photo and post in news circle.
### Other
*	Receive data from Internet
*	View network connections
*	Full network access
*	Prevent device from sleeping

These permissions enable News Pro to collect anonymous usage data. This usage data helps us to further improve the performance of News Pro by keeping track of crashes and exceptions.
It is enabled by default when user downloads app from Google Play. It can be disabled or enabled from settings page as per the convenience of the user.

### What information does News Pro obtain and how is it used?
News Crow may collect certain  anonymous usage data automatically, including, but not limited to, the type of mobile device you use, your mobile devices unique device ID, the IP address of your mobile device, your mobile operating system, the type of mobile Internet browsers you use, and information about the way you use our app.
Note that this data does not include private and privileged information like Username, Email, Phone number, Address etc. Such private information is not shared to any third party.

### What are my opt-out rights?
User can opt out from sharing usage data with the developer from the settings page. User can disabled or enable the "Usage Statistics" from settings page as per the convenience of the user.

### Does App collect precise real time location information of the device?
App does collect precise information about the location of your mobile device for future usage and provide curated news.

### Do third parties see and/or have access to information obtained by the Application?
No. Third parties have no access whatsoever to the information generated through the medium of App.

### Children
We do not use our app to knowingly solicit any data from or market to children under the age of 13.

### Security
We are concerned about safeguarding the confidentiality of your information. App requires for and asks for permissions to access only the absolutely necessary functionality of the user's device like Camera, Storage and Internet.  These permissions if granted operate only in the domain of the user's device and no private information is shared to the developer, third party or anywhere else.

### Changes
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for any reason. We will notify you of any changes to our Privacy Policy by posting the new Privacy Policy here and inside the app. You are advised to consult this Privacy Policy regularly for any changes, as continued use is deemed approval of all changes.

### Contact us
If you have any questions regarding privacy while using this app, or have questions about our practices, please contact us via email at <a href="mailto:colthurling@gmail.com">colthurling@gmail.com</a>.

